title: Some great judges and audience
selftext:
Some amazing judges too

This guy is not indian but just look at the beauty of judges and and audience... Everyone just keeps quiet and only you can hear is the performer. Apne India mei banda saans leta hai and judges be like " wooooooo" shouting into the microphone ....
